2001年9月11日早晨，19名劫機者分别控制四架民航客机。这四架客机从[[波士顿|波士顿]]、[[纽瓦克_(新泽西州)|-{zh-cn:纽瓦克;zh-tw:紐華克;zh-hk:紐瓦克}-]]和[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]（[[华盛顿杜勒斯国际机场|华盛顿杜勒斯国际机场]]）飞往[[旧金山|旧金山]]和[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]<ref name="SecCounc" />。上午8:46（標準時間上午7:46），[[美国航空11号班机|美国航空11号班机]]撞向世贸中心北座大楼，接着[[联合航空175号班机|联合航空175号班机]]于上午9:03（標準時間上午8:03）衝向南座大楼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight_%20Path_%20Study_AA11.pdf |title=Flight Path Study - American Airlines Flight 11 |publisher=National Transportation Safety Board |date=2002-02-19 |format=pdf |access-date=2009-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201053016/http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight_%20Path_%20Study_AA11.pdf |archive-date=2009-02-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight_%20Path%20_Study_UA175.pdf |title=Flight Path Study - United Airlines Flight 175 |publisher=National Transportation Safety Board |date=2002-02-19 |format=pdf |access-date=2009-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225172436/http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight_%20Path%20_Study_UA175.pdf%20 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。上午9:37（標準時間8:37），另一组劫机者控制[[美国航空77号班机|美国航空77号班机]]撞入[[五角大楼|五角大楼]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight_%20Path_%20Study_AA77.pdf |title=Flight Path Study - American Airlines Flight 77 |publisher=National Transportation Safety Board |date=2002-02-19 |format=pdf |access-date=2009-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225172304/http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight_%20Path_%20Study_AA77.pdf%20 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第四架飞机——[[联合航空93号班机|联合航空93号班机]]的最终目标被认为是[[美国国会大厦|美国国会大厦]]或者是[[白宫|白宫]]，在机上乘客与劫机者搏斗后，这架飞机于上午10:03（標準時間上午9:03）在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]的[[尚克斯维尔|尚克斯维尔]]附近坠毁<ref name="Chap7">{{cite book |chapter=The Attack Looms |url=http://govinfo.library.unt.edu/911/report/911Report_Ch7.htm |year=2004 |title=9/11 Commission Report |publisher=National Commission on Terrorist Attacks Upon the United States |accessdate=2008-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225172128/http://govinfo.library.unt.edu/911/report/911Report_Ch7.htm%20 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight%20_Path_%20Study_UA93.pdf |title=Flight Path Study - United Airlines Flight 93 |publisher=National Transportation Safety Board |date=2002-02-19 |format=pdf |access-date=2009-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225172644/http://www.ntsb.gov/info/Flight%20_Path_%20Study_UA93.pdf%20 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至於紐約受到飛機襲擊的世貿中心群，其中南塔於上午9:59（標準時間上午8:59）倒塌，北塔則於10:28（標準時間上午9:28）從上到下坍塌，其他受到波及的建築物包含[[德意志银行大厦|德意志銀行大廈]]、西街90號、[[萬豪酒店|萬豪酒店]]、[[威訊大樓|威訊大樓]]、[[美國海關及邊境保衛局|美國海關]]、[[希爾頓酒店|希爾頓酒店]]、紐約電話大樓、[[世界贸易中心圣尼古拉国家朝圣地|希臘正教會聖尼古拉堂]]等多棟重要機構與建築。下午5:20（標準時間下午4:20）因北塔的重型碎片間接產生火勢，導致北塔旁的[[世貿中心七號大樓|世貿中心七號大樓]]倒塌，並沒有造成額外的人員傷亡，但也造成當地無法修復的嚴重的破壞和污染。

在劫机过程中，劫机者使用刀槍殺害[[飞行员|飞行员]]、[[空中乘务员|-{zh-hans:空中乘务员;zh-hant:空服員}-]]和乘客。飞机上与外界取得联系的乘客报告称，劫机者使用刀刺伤-{zh-hans:乘务员;zh-hant:空服員}-，并且在其中两次劫机事件中至少有一名乘客被刺伤<ref name=911-ch1>{{cite book|url=http://www.9-11commission.gov/report/911Report_Ch1.pdf|title=9/11 Commission Report|chapter=Chapter 1.1: 'We Have Some Planes': Inside the Four Flights|year=2004|publisher=National Commission on Terrorist Attacks Upon the United States|accessdate=2009-04-22|format=PDF|pages=4-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100923071807/http://www.9-11commission.gov/report/911Report_Ch1.pdf|archive-date=2010-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0201/06/lklw.00.html |title=Encore Presentation: Barbara Olson Remembered |work=Larry King Live |publisher=CNN |date=2002-01-06 |accessdate=2008-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225172447/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0201/06/lklw.00.html%20 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有一些乘客设法使用机舱电话和手机与外界取得联系<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/headlines/20010916phonecallnat3p3.asp |title=The phone line from Flight 93 was still open when a GTE operator heard Todd Beamer say: 'Are you guys ready? Let's roll' |publisher=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |date=2001-09-16 |author=McKinnon, Jim |accessdate=2008-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118015531/http://www.post-gazette.com/headlines/20010916phonecallnat3p3.asp |archive-date=2012-01-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://archives.cnn.com/2001/US/09/12/family.reacts/index.html |title=Relatives wait for news as rescuers dig |publisher=CNN |date=2001-09-13 |accessdate=2008-05-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080522050524/http://archives.cnn.com/2001/US/09/12/family.reacts/index.html |archivedate=2008-05-22 }}</ref>，并提供有关劫机的一些细节。这些细节包括：
* 每架飞机上都有多名劫机者；
* 劫机者使用[[胡椒噴霧|胡椒噴霧]]或者其他有毒化学喷雾器，例如[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]；
